notes: Iraq (Erbil) profiling of urban/out-of-camp IDPs, Syrian refugees, and host populations with data collected from Dec 2015 until January 2016 (report published June 2016). The exercise included a household survey administered to a sample of 1,163 households (403 IDP, 370 refugee and 390 host households). Data can also be explored through the DART: http://www.dart.jips.org/.
